<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٥٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَبْدِ اللهِ <span class="special">﵄</span> وَهُوَ يَطُوفُ بِالْبَيْتِ أَنَهَى رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> عَنْ صِيَامِ يَوْمِ الْجُمُعَةِ؟<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> نَعَمْ، وَرَبِّ هَذَا الْبَيْتِ .»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>